706
00:23:24,840 --> 00:23:25,880
 Iznutra,

707
00:23:25,880 --> 00:23:26,560
 kaže,

708
00:23:26,560 --> 00:23:27,600
 ovo je toliki dar od Boga.

709
00:23:27,600 --> 00:23:28,820
 A dok sam slušao nju,

710
00:23:28,820 --> 00:23:30,280
 te njezine riječi,

711
00:23:30,280 --> 00:23:33,280
 osjećao sam kako su meni upalile ovu želju

712
00:23:33,280 --> 00:23:35,300
 da izađem iz ove moje

713
00:23:35,300 --> 00:23:38,500
 pogrešne ispunjenosti,

714
00:23:38,500 --> 00:23:40,340
 koje mislim da ću biti ispunjen,

715
00:23:40,340 --> 00:23:41,080
 ne znam,

716
00:23:41,080 --> 00:23:43,700
 sa igračkama ovog svijeta,

717
00:23:43,700 --> 00:23:45,340
 a zapravo ostanem prazan.

718
00:23:45,340 --> 00:23:45,940
 Evo,

719
00:23:45,940 --> 00:23:47,040
 pročitat ću vam za kraj

720
00:23:47,040 --> 00:23:48,400
 jednu poeziju,

721
00:23:48,400 --> 00:23:49,200
 može jedna poezija.

722
00:23:49,200 --> 00:23:49,920
 Inače,

723
00:23:49,920 --> 00:23:51,500
 te poezije mogu biti dosadne,

724
00:23:51,500 --> 00:23:53,180
 neki ljudi samo pišu knjige poezija,

725
00:23:53,180 --> 00:23:53,960
 pa dave druge.

726
00:23:53,960 --> 00:23:56,640
 To je istina,

727
00:23:56,640 --> 00:23:58,500
 ali poezija ima u sebi,

728
00:23:58,500 --> 00:23:59,480
 ako je dobra,

729
00:23:59,480 --> 00:24:00,160
 a ova je dobra,

730
00:24:00,160 --> 00:24:02,820
 da u malo riječi izrazi bit.

731
00:24:02,820 --> 00:24:03,020
 Evo,

732
00:24:03,020 --> 00:24:04,040
 ako me ništa nisi čuo,

733
00:24:04,040 --> 00:24:05,400
 ja se nadam da ova poezija

734
00:24:05,400 --> 00:24:07,000
 od Frabonaventure Dude,

735
00:24:07,000 --> 00:24:08,380
 ko zna koje je Frabonaventure,

736
00:24:08,380 --> 00:24:09,040
 umore nedavno,

737
00:24:09,040 --> 00:24:10,280
 jedan sveti Franjevac,

738
00:24:10,820 --> 00:24:12,840
 kad imate one Biblije Hrvatske,

739
00:24:12,840 --> 00:24:14,060
 onda uvijek piše njegovo ime,

740
00:24:14,060 --> 00:24:15,480
 on je bio vrsan prevoditelj,

741
00:24:15,480 --> 00:24:16,620
 poznavatelj jezika,

742
00:24:16,620 --> 00:24:18,560
 teologije i tako dalje.

743
00:24:18,560 --> 00:24:19,080
 Evo,

744
00:24:19,080 --> 00:24:21,640
 jedna poezija kratka,

745
00:24:21,640 --> 00:24:22,720
 koja se nadam da će,

746
00:24:22,720 --> 00:24:24,600
 meni je dotakla neke žice duše,

747
00:24:24,600 --> 00:24:28,480
 koje teško doseći,

748
00:24:28,480 --> 00:24:29,740
 baš me dotakla,

749
00:24:29,740 --> 00:24:30,680
 jer govori istinu o nama,

750
00:24:30,680 --> 00:24:32,080
 on se tu malo,

751
00:24:32,080 --> 00:24:34,200
 Božje ime je ja jesam,

752
00:24:34,200 --> 00:24:36,840
 i Krist kad su došli po njega,

753
00:24:36,840 --> 00:24:39,100
 onda Krist je rekao ja jesam,

754
00:24:39,160 --> 00:24:42,100
 smo su popadali po zemlji u Gecemaniju,

755
00:24:42,100 --> 00:24:44,000
 a namjerno evanđelist piše,

756
00:24:44,000 --> 00:24:45,040
 kako Petar kaže,

757
00:24:45,040 --> 00:24:46,440
 ti si bio s tim čovjekom,

758
00:24:46,440 --> 00:24:46,940
 nisam,

759
00:24:46,940 --> 00:24:47,660
 ja nisam,

760
00:24:47,660 --> 00:24:49,440
 on kaže tri puta nisam,

761
00:24:49,440 --> 00:24:50,540
 a mišlja da jeste,

762
00:24:50,540 --> 00:24:52,120
 da će on s njime u zatvor,

763
00:24:52,120 --> 00:24:52,680
 da će on s njime,

764
00:24:52,680 --> 00:24:53,720
 mišlja da jeste,

765
00:24:53,720 --> 00:24:54,420
 a vidio i da nije,

766
00:24:54,420 --> 00:24:55,960
 onda se on s njime malo s tim,

767
00:24:55,960 --> 00:24:57,180
 jesam, nisam igra,

768
00:24:57,180 --> 00:24:57,900
 evo,

769
00:24:57,900 --> 00:24:59,120
 jeste spremni za jednu poeziju,

770
00:24:59,120 --> 00:24:59,480
 evo,

771
00:24:59,480 --> 00:25:00,400
 niste navikli baš to,

772
00:25:00,400 --> 00:25:01,440
 ali mene je takla,

773
00:25:01,440 --> 00:25:03,600
 nada se da će i vas taknuti,

774
00:25:03,720 --> 00:25:04,620
 i ulit vam unutra,

775
00:25:04,620 --> 00:25:07,200
 oživit vas iznutra.

776
00:25:07,200 --> 00:25:09,920
 Kaže fra Bonaventura,

777
00:25:09,920 --> 00:25:11,360
 Duda otkriva na svoju dušu,

778
00:25:11,360 --> 00:25:14,000
 uvijek sam volio mjeseći,

779
00:25:14,000 --> 00:25:16,580
 u njoj sve stvari se čine,

780
00:25:16,580 --> 00:25:18,200
 kao da jesu,

781
00:25:18,200 --> 00:25:19,820
 i kao da nisu,

782
00:25:19,820 --> 00:25:22,800
 i sebi sam tako izgledam,

783
00:25:22,800 --> 00:25:23,800
 da jesam,

784
00:25:23,800 --> 00:25:25,520
 i kao da nisam,

785
00:25:26,940 --> 00:25:28,200
 i kad mislim da jesam,

786
00:25:28,200 --> 00:25:30,440
 skoro želim da nisam,

787
00:25:30,440 --> 00:25:33,300
 jer ja koji jesam,

788
00:25:33,300 --> 00:25:35,540
 više sam onaj koji nisam,

789
00:25:35,540 --> 00:25:39,360
 i moglo bi biti da k Bogu dođem,

790
00:25:39,360 --> 00:25:40,240
 kao da jesam,

791
00:25:40,240 --> 00:25:44,020
 a On će mi reći da nisam,

792
00:25:44,020 --> 00:25:47,520
 a tada bolje bi bilo da me nije ni bilo,

793
00:25:47,520 --> 00:25:50,240
 a kad mislim da nisam,

794
00:25:50,240 --> 00:25:51,040
 bude mi žal,

795
00:25:51,040 --> 00:25:53,100
 jer želim da jesam,

796
00:25:53,100 --> 00:25:55,940
 o kako je dobro biti,

797
00:25:56,740 --> 00:25:58,000
 to možda i ne znam pravo,

798
00:25:58,000 --> 00:25:59,000
 već samo slutim,

799
00:25:59,000 --> 00:26:00,260
 kako je dobro biti,

800
00:26:00,260 --> 00:26:02,540
 jer ono malo što jesam,

801
00:26:02,540 --> 00:26:03,660
 dok nisam,

802
00:26:03,660 --> 00:26:05,560
 kako je lijepo biti,

803
00:26:05,560 --> 00:26:07,920
 o ti koji jesi,

804
00:26:07,920 --> 00:26:09,380
 i nikada nisi,

805
00:26:09,380 --> 00:26:11,100
 o daj mi biti,

806
00:26:11,100 --> 00:26:12,100
 biti mi daj,

807
00:26:12,100 --> 00:26:13,600
 da jesam,

808
00:26:13,600 --> 00:26:15,620
 i samo jesam vječno,

809
00:26:15,620 --> 00:26:17,340
 i zauvijek jesam u tebi,

810
00:26:17,340 --> 00:26:19,340
 o ti koji jesi,

811
00:26:19,340 --> 00:26:20,820
 biti mi daj.

812
00:26:20,820 --> 00:26:23,400
 Eto, to je Bonaventura Duda,

813
00:26:23,400 --> 00:26:24,840
 jedan put jedan učitelj u školi,

814
00:26:24,840 --> 00:26:25,720
 pitao to djeci,

815
00:26:25,720 --> 00:26:26,640
 onda je mali pitao,

816
00:26:26,700 --> 00:26:28,180
 a na kraju,

817
00:26:28,180 --> 00:26:29,880
 jesi li ti ili nisi.

